sequenceDiagram
    participant HR as HR User
    participant FE as Frontend
    participant BE as Backend
    participant AI as Matching Service
    participant DB as Database
    
    HR->>FE: Search CVs for Position
    FE->>BE: GET /api/pool-cvs?positionId=xxx
    BE->>AI: Calculate Match Scores
    AI->>DB: Load Position Requirements
    AI->>DB: Load CV Skills/Languages
    AI->>AI: Calculate Compatibility
    AI->>BE: Return Match Scores
    BE->>FE: Return CVs with Scores
    FE->>HR: Display Matched CVs
    HR->>FE: Select CV to Match
    FE->>BE: POST /api/pool-cvs/:id/positions/:id/match
    BE->>DB: Create CvPositionMatch
    BE->>DB: Create Application
    BE->>FE: Success Response
    FE->>HR: Show Success Message

